PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of MICHELE McKENZIE, of Halifax, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Robert Thompson, who has resigned.
